# 4. Batch Apex Interface

Every Batch class implements

```apex
Database.Batchable<SObject>
```

Example

```apex
global class UpdateAccountBatch implements Database.Batchable<SObject>
{
}
```

This interface forces us to implement

```
start()

execute()

finish()
```

