# 6. start()

Purpose

Tell Salesforce

> Which records should I process?

Example

```apex
global Database.QueryLocator start(Database.BatchableContext bc)
{
    return Database.getQueryLocator(
        'SELECT Id, Name FROM Account'
    );
}
```

Salesforce stores this query.

Later it divides the records.

---

Why QueryLocator?

Normal SOQL

```
50,000 records
```

Batch QueryLocator

```
50 Million records
```

Huge difference.

