# 13. QueryLocator vs Iterable

## QueryLocator

```apex
return Database.getQueryLocator(
'SELECT Id FROM Account');
```

Advantages

✔ Up to

```
50 Million
```

records.

Recommended most of the time.

---

## Iterable

Instead of SOQL

You create records yourself.

Example

```apex
global Iterable<Account> start(...)
```

Useful when

* Records come from API
* Records come from multiple queries
* Custom collection

Rarely used.

